00:00:29,846 --> 00:00:33,942
It's 7.:00 a.m., children, and you're listening
to Radio-Free Harvard...

2
00:00:34,051 --> 00:00:36,077
...on a chilly November morning.

3
00:00:36,186 --> 00:00:39,679
